Story: Some story about email

  As a group member
  I want to receive email from my fellow group members
  So that I might participate in their endeavors
  
  Scenario: group member receives question in email
  
    Given a user named Mississippi
    And a user named Bobcatt
    And a group called Freewheelers
    And Mississippi is a member of Freewheelers
    And Bobcatt is a member of Freewheelers
    When Bobcatt asks a question of the Freewheelers group
    Then Mississippi should receive an email
    And the email should contain Bobcatt's question